NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
L.M.S., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
B.M., Defendant. In the Matter of the Guardianship of R.S.-M., a Minor-Respondent. C-635 September Term 2018
081272 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004515-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
